Description_lang: The One-Armed Bandit rolls a massive casino chip towards players, causing anyone caught in its path to become $@spellname460430. Players can stand near the path to become a $@spellname460444. Upon reaching its destination, the chip then falls over and inflicts $460424s1 Nature damage to players within $460635A1 yards with an additional $460427s1 Nature damage to all players.Players may roll these chips back to destroy them.
